            "id": 6397355,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 創見(2451)大跌7.06%，報237元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>創見(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2451:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2451\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2451-TW</a>)26日10:40股價下跌18元，報237.0元，跌幅7.06%，成交1,945張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>創見(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2451:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2451\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2451-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為電腦等數位產品之記憶體擴充卡。電腦週邊產品。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌19.3%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌5.06%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-1,487 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-3,641 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+2,923 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-769 張</li> <li>融資增減：-1,936 張</li> <li>融券增減：-223 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
